Author Post!


11 Jun 2019 01:59






So many people fuckin helped critique this thing I swear it was half the site lol. But for real, I don’t even feel like coding the names so Ihp, Ayers, TheBlueHour, RadioactiveRADS, Caspin2, UraniumEmpire, TheMightyMcB, and anyone else I forgot to thank because so many fucking people helped. And BIG thanks to Attila, because well— he’s my co-author! I was desperate, at the happiest place on earth, Disney World down in the dumps (so bad my family noticed, I had to continually convince them I was fine) because a piece I’d been working on for months was failing. I was eating dinner, and I pulled out my phone, and saw a forum thread I posted calling out for help got attention by Attila the Pun who said he’d co-author the article with me. My spirits lifted. Seriously Attila, you don’t know how greatful I am for your help. We both worked this week to pick this piece back up, and here it is! Thank you so much!





